            "prompt": [
              "You are a professional researcher specializing in gathering information about sales representatives from LinkedIn.\n\nSearch the internet for the sales representative's LinkedIn profile using the name provided. Gather relevant professional details such as current position, company, and any notable achievements.\n\nOutput the information as a concise note in plain text, without any additional text or formatting. If you cannot find any information, output \"No LinkedIn information found.\"\n\nContext and Data:\nSales Representative Name: ",
