        {
          "type": "aiText",
          "options": {
            "referencedFieldIds": [
              "fld3Nuhl1y5BLAVI5"
            ],
            "prompt": [
              "You are an expert document analyst tasked with reviewing file attachments to extract a concise and relevant title that best summarizes the main subject or purpose. Maintain a professional and objective tone, ensuring the title is informative and clear.\n\nTask description:\nCarefully examine the attached file(s) for key phrases, headings, or content that indicate the primary topic, objective, or main focus. If there are multiple files, select a title that accurately represents the overarching theme or purpose shared among them. The title should be brief, specific, and informative, avoiding generic terms or redundancy. If a clear title cannot be identified, use your judgment to create the most representative one possible.\n\nOutput format:\nOutput a single, concise title in plain text containing only the relevant keywords or phrase. Do not include any additional text, explanations, the file name, or formatting. If no reasonable title can be generated from the file(s), output \"Unable to determine title from file content.\" Example: \"Employee Onboarding Checklist\" (real examples may vary in length/content depending on the file subject).\n\nContext and Data:\nFile Content: ",
              {
                "field": {
                  "fieldId": "fld3Nuhl1y5BLAVI5"
                }
              },
              "\n\nOutput:\n"
            ]
          },
          "id": "fldHgjsUktcToAorE",
          "name": "Extracted Title (File Content)"
        }
